310 static void *DPC_ObjDetDSP_MemPoolAlloc(MemPoolObj *pool,
311  uint32_t size,
312  uint8_t align)
313 {
314  void *retAddr = NULL;
315  uintptr_t addr;
316 
317  addr = MEM_ALIGN(pool->currAddr, align);
318  if ((addr + size) <= ((uintptr_t)pool->cfg.addr + pool->cfg.size))
319  {
320  retAddr = (void *)addr;
321  pool->currAddr = addr + size;
322  pool->maxCurrAddr = MAX(pool->currAddr, pool->maxCurrAddr);
323  }
324 
325  return(retAddr);
326 }

415 void DPC_ObjectDetection_chirpEvent (DPM_DPCHandle handle)
416 {
417  ObjDetObj *objDetObj = (ObjDetObj *) handle;
418  uint32_t margin;
419 
420  if(objDetObj->chirpIndex != 0)
421  {
422  margin = Cycleprofiler_getTimeStamp() - objDetObj->chirpEndTime;
423  if(margin < objDetObj->chirpMargin)
424  {
425  /* Find the smallest margin to report as chirp margin */
426  objDetObj->chirpMargin = margin;
427  }
428  }
429  else
430  {
431  /* Reset margin min */
432  objDetObj->chirpMargin = 0xffffffff;
433  }
434 
435  /* Notify the DPM Module that the DPC is ready for execution */
436  DebugP_assert (DPM_notifyExecute (objDetObj->dpmHandle, handle, true) == 0);
437 
438  return;
439 }

666 static void DPC_ObjDetDSP_quadFit(float *x, float*y, float *xv, float *yv)
667 {
668  float a, b, c, denom;
669  float x0 = x[0];
670  float x1 = x[1];
671  float x2 = x[2];
672  float y0 = y[0];
673  float y1 = y[1];
674  float y2 = y[2];
675 
676  denom = (x0 - x1)*(x0 - x2)*(x1 - x2);
677  a = (x2 * (y1 - y0) + x1 * (y0 - y2) + x0 * (y2 - y1)) / denom;
678  b = (x2*x2 * (y0 - y1) + x1*x1 * (y2 - y0) + x0*x0 * (y1 - y2)) / denom;
679  c = (x1 * x2 * (x1 - x2) * y0 + x2 * x0 * (x2 - x0) * y1 + x0 * x1 * (x0 - x1) * y2) / denom;
680 
681  *xv = -b/(2 * a);
682  *yv = c - b*b/(4 * a);
683 }

702 static void DPC_ObjDetDSP_rangeBiasRxChPhaseMeasure
703 (
704  DPC_ObjectDetection_StaticCfg *staticCfg,
705  float targetDistance,
706  float searchWinSize,
707  uint16_t *detMatrix,
708  uint32_t *symbolMatrix,
709  DPU_AoAProc_compRxChannelBiasCfg *compRxChanCfg
710 )
711 {
712  cmplx16ImRe_t rxSym[SYS_COMMON_NUM_TX_ANTENNAS * SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL];
713  cmplx16ImRe_t *tempPtr;
714  float sumSqr;
715  uint32_t * rxSymPtr = (uint32_t * ) rxSym;
716  float xMagSq[SYS_COMMON_NUM_TX_ANTENNAS * SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL];
717  int32_t iMax;
718  float xMagSqMin;
719  float scal;
720  float truePosition;
721  int32_t truePositionIndex;
722  float y[3];
723  float x[3];
724  int32_t halfWinSize ;
725  float estPeakPos;
726  float estPeakVal;
727  int32_t i, ind;
728  int32_t txIdx, rxIdx;
729 
730  uint32_t numRxAntennas = staticCfg->ADCBufData.dataProperty.numRxAntennas;
731  uint32_t numTxAntennas = staticCfg->numTxAntennas;
732  uint32_t numRangeBins = staticCfg->numRangeBins;
733  uint32_t numDopplerChirps = staticCfg->numDopplerChirps;
734  uint32_t numSymPerTxAnt = numDopplerChirps * numRxAntennas * numRangeBins;
735  uint32_t symbolMatrixIndx;
736 
737  uint16_t maxVal = 0;
738 
739  truePosition = targetDistance / staticCfg->rangeStep;
740  truePositionIndex = (int32_t) (truePosition + 0.5);
741 
742  halfWinSize = (int32_t) (0.5 * searchWinSize / staticCfg->rangeStep + 0.5);
743 
744  /**** Range calibration ****/
745  iMax = truePositionIndex;
746  for (i = truePositionIndex - halfWinSize; i <= truePositionIndex + halfWinSize; i++)
747  {
748  if (detMatrix[i * staticCfg->numDopplerBins] > maxVal)
749  {
750  maxVal = detMatrix[i * staticCfg->numDopplerBins];
751  iMax = i;
752  }
753  }
754 
755  /* Fine estimate of the peak position using quadratic fit */
756  ind = 0;
757  for (i = iMax - 1; i <= iMax + 1; i++)
758  {
759  sumSqr = 0.0;
760  for (txIdx=0; txIdx < numTxAntennas; txIdx++)
761  {
762  for (rxIdx=0; rxIdx < numRxAntennas; rxIdx++)
763  {
764  symbolMatrixIndx = txIdx * numSymPerTxAnt + rxIdx * numRangeBins + i;
765  tempPtr = (cmplx16ImRe_t *) &symbolMatrix[symbolMatrixIndx];
766  sumSqr += (float) tempPtr->real * (float) tempPtr->real +
767  (float) tempPtr->imag * (float) tempPtr->imag;
768  }
769  }
770 #ifdef SUBSYS_DSS
771  y[ind] = sqrtsp(sumSqr);
772 #else
773  y[ind] = sqrt(sumSqr);
774 #endif
775  x[ind] = (float)i;
776  ind++;
777  }
778  DPC_ObjDetDSP_quadFit(x, y, &estPeakPos, &estPeakVal);
779  compRxChanCfg->rangeBias = (estPeakPos - truePosition) * staticCfg->rangeStep;
780 
781  /*** Calculate Rx channel phase/gain compensation coefficients ***/
782  for (txIdx = 0; txIdx < numTxAntennas; txIdx++)
783  {
784  for (rxIdx = 0; rxIdx < numRxAntennas; rxIdx++)
785  {
786  i = txIdx * numRxAntennas + rxIdx;
787  symbolMatrixIndx = txIdx * numSymPerTxAnt + rxIdx * numRangeBins + iMax;
788  rxSymPtr[i] = symbolMatrix[symbolMatrixIndx];
789  xMagSq[i] = (float) rxSym[i].real * (float) rxSym[i].real +
790  (float) rxSym[i].imag * (float) rxSym[i].imag;
791  }
792  }
793  xMagSqMin = xMagSq[0];
794  for (i = 1; i < staticCfg->numVirtualAntennas; i++)
795  {
796  if (xMagSq[i] < xMagSqMin)
797  {
798  xMagSqMin = xMagSq[i];
799  }
800  }
801 
802  for (txIdx=0; txIdx < staticCfg->numTxAntennas; txIdx++)
803  {
804  for (rxIdx=0; rxIdx < numRxAntennas; rxIdx++)
805  {
806  int32_t temp;
807  i = txIdx * numRxAntennas + rxIdx;
808  scal = 32768./ xMagSq[i] * sqrt(xMagSqMin);
809 
810  temp = (int32_t) MATHUTILS_ROUND_FLOAT(scal * rxSym[i].real);
811  MATHUTILS_SATURATE16(temp);
812  compRxChanCfg->rxChPhaseComp[staticCfg->txAntOrder[txIdx] * numRxAntennas +
813  rxIdx].real = (int16_t) (temp);
814 
815  temp = (int32_t) MATHUTILS_ROUND_FLOAT(-scal * rxSym[i].imag);
816  MATHUTILS_SATURATE16(temp);
817  compRxChanCfg->rxChPhaseComp[staticCfg->txAntOrder[txIdx] * numRxAntennas
818  + rxIdx].imag = (int16_t) (temp);
819  }
820  }
821 }

851 static uint32_t DPC_ObjDetDSP_GenDopplerWindow
852 (
853  DPU_DopplerProcDSP_Config *cfg
854 )
855 {
856  uint32_t winType;
857 
858  /* For too small window, force rectangular window to avoid loss of information
859  * due to small window values (e.g. hanning has first and last coefficients 0) */
860  if (cfg->staticCfg.numDopplerChirps <= 4)
861  {
862  winType = MMWAVELIB_WIN_RECT;
863  }
864  else
865  {
866  winType = DPC_DPU_DOPPLERPROC_FFT_WINDOW_TYPE;
867  }
868  DPC_ObjDetDSP_genWindow((void *)cfg->hwRes.windowCoeff,
869  MMWAVELIB_WINDOW_INT32,
870  cfg->staticCfg.numDopplerChirps,
871  DPC_ObjDetDSP_GetDopplerWinGenLen(cfg->staticCfg.numDopplerChirps),
872  DPC_OBJDET_QFORMAT_DOPPLER_FFT,
873  winType);
874  return(winType);
875 }

892 static void DPC_ObjDetDSP_GetRxChPhaseComp(DPC_ObjectDetection_StaticCfg *staticCfg,
893  DPU_AoAProc_compRxChannelBiasCfg *inpCfg,
894  DPU_AoAProc_compRxChannelBiasCfg *outCfg)
895 {
896  uint32_t tx, rx, numTxAnt, numRxAnt;
897  uint8_t *txAntOrder, *rxAntOrder;
898  cmplx16ImRe_t one;
899 
900  one.imag = 0;
901  one.real = 0x7fff;
902 
903  numTxAnt = staticCfg->numTxAntennas;
904  numRxAnt = staticCfg->ADCBufData.dataProperty.numRxAntennas;
905  txAntOrder = staticCfg->txAntOrder;

907  outCfg->rangeBias = inpCfg->rangeBias;

909  for(tx = 0; tx < numTxAnt; tx++)
910  {
911  for(rx = 0; rx < numRxAnt; rx++)
912  {
913  if (staticCfg->isValidProfileHasOneTxPerChirp == 1U)
914  {
915  outCfg->rxChPhaseComp[tx * numRxAnt + rx] =
916  inpCfg->rxChPhaseComp[txAntOrder[tx] * SYS_COMMON_NUM_RX_CHANNEL +
917  rxAntOrder[rx]];
918  }
919  else
920  {
921  outCfg->rxChPhaseComp[tx * numRxAnt + rx] = one;
922  }
923  }
924  }
